data.title: Garage Door Peek Rendezvous to C Site
data.description: Here's an easy, yet powerful way to aggressively peek Garage at the start of the round.

data.title: A Site Trademark + Top A Site Rendezvous
data.description: Use this powerful setup to gain early information towards A Lobby, while repositioning yourself to an aggressive off-angle. The trademark will activate for both A Short and A Long.

data.title: Aggressive A Short Rendezvous to A Link
data.description: Use this Rendezvous to make aggressive plays in A Short, or even work with a teammate to gather information in A Lobby from A Long so that you can hold a line from A Short that allows you to lock that area of the map down for your team.

data.title: C Site Rendezvous for Top of C Default
data.description: Here's a simple, but effective Rendezvous for Top of C Default.
